<p>Thresher's main page is a simple page with a welcome message and links to the most recently created and most recently updated wiki pages. Like other welcome messages, Thresher's welcome message can be changed from the Site Messages page.</p>

<p>Thresher's main page includes a list of the 10 most recently updated wiki pages. This is a good reference to see what kinds of changes have been made recently and who made the changes along with a link to the wiki page. If the user who made the change offered a change comment, that comment about their change will be seen to the right of the link.</p>

<p>Finally, Thresher's main page includes a list of the 10 most recently created wiki pages. This is a good reference to see what kinds of pages have been created recently and who created the page along with a link to the wiki page. If the user who created the page put a summary in, the summary will be seen to the right of the link.</p>